Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.22,0:01:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久违的牧场
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.77,0:01:50.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得 到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.80,0:01:51.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.35,0:01:58.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦你了 彼得 路上小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.39,0:01:59.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.69,0:02:46.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.89,0:02:50.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年就拜托你了\N恩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.56,0:02:51.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 彼得
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.34,0:02:55.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年羊也拜托你照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.31,0:02:57.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.45,0:04:06.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.19,0:04:09.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 今天起的很早嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.81,0:04:10.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.94,0:04:15.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约瑟夫 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:29.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿白 黑熊 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.06,0:04:37.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要上山了 高兴么 我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.12,0:04:53.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.96,0:05:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得带着羊群来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.29,0:05:08.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.94,0:05:34.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海蒂 不要玩的太疯\N要是受伤了就不可以去牧场了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.12,0:05:36.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.71,0:05:44.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼 彼得\N海蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.80,0:05:55.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.41,0:06:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没忘记我吧 还记得我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:01.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿托莉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.18,0:06:05.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有凶小子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.22,0:06:11.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都来了 谁都不少
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.20,0:06:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得 小雪 阿托莉 凶小子\N还有其他的羊 都还记得我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.67,0:06:20.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是当然的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.95,0:06:22.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 海蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.46,0:06:37.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.79,0:06:40.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 老爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.57,0:06:44.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大将军 今年也拜托你了\N恩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.43,0:06:49.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是海蒂的便当 她太专注忘记拿了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:52.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得 快点来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.90,0:07:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有我要去村里一下 估计你们下山的时候\N应该能回来 不过你还是告诉海蒂一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.50,0:07:02.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.91,0:07:31.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,松鼠 是松鼠\N恩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.08,0:07:37.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们看起来好开心啊 因为春天的原因吧\N是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.10,0:07:57.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啾啾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.06,0:07:59.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里？哪个是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.64,0:08:05.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啾啾 啾啾 啾啾 是我啊 啾啾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.69,0:08:29.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啾啾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.27,0:08:46.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啾啾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.43,0:09:27.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啾啾 啾啾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:33.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得 果然是啾啾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.68,0:09:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪个是啾啾 那么多鸟儿不可能认得出吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.90,0:09:41.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是 每一只都是啾啾哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:45.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是？\N对啊 它们都是啾啾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.76,0:09:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.18,0:10:05.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啾啾\N啾啾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.62,0:10:22.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.28,0:10:49.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岩石和旗子 和去年一样还在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.81,0:10:51.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海蒂 你跑的太急了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.01,0:10:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:30.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹰 是鹰 彼得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.09,0:11:39.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹰 好精神的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.07,0:11:52.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直独自飞翔在高空
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.23,0:11:56.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 雪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.07,0:12:06.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好凉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.70,0:12:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是小可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.53,0:12:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小宝宝 是小可爱的小宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.93,0:12:36.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道老大在不在 大角老大在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.35,0:12:49.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有好多残雪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.00,0:13:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老大 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.63,0:13:55.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.68,0:13:59.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.98,0:14:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪 去哪里了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.88,0:14:10.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海蒂 海蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.45,0:14:14.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.54,0:14:23.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海蒂 你去哪里了 我好担心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:26.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.49,0:14:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是给彼得的 我给你带上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.39,0:14:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 我不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.58,0:14:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要不行 特意为你做的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.00,0:14:47.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好看啊 彼得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.90,0:14:51.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是么 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.75,0:14:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是特别的日子 是春天到来的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:15:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海蒂 我去给大家都带上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.03,0:15:03.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.69,0:15:06.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 给
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.91,0:15:11.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.09,0:15:16.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿托莉 阿托莉 给
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.34,0:15:24.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.36,0:15:29.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿白 这是你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.41,0:15:34.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿白 这么开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.06,0:15:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一 二 三
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.66,0:15:56.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得 大家好开心啊 都喜欢我的花环
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.31,0:15:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.53,0:16:10.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.86,0:16:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海蒂 快到岩蓬那边去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.04,0:17:51.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨停了\N恩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.38,0:18:02.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 这只羊是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.80,0:18:06.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得 这只羊怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:09.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 我没见过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.98,0:18:12.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陌生的小羊啊 你从哪里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.52,0:18:20.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小七 小七
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.87,0:18:24.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是在刚刚的雨中迷路了 一定在找它呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.61,0:18:26.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是它会是哪里的羊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.93,0:18:32.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是隔壁村里的 回到村子里应该就能知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.35,0:18:34.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们回去么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.41,0:18:36.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小七
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.19,0:18:41.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小七
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.37,0:18:43.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来接你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.02,0:18:47.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙 害我担心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.91,0:18:49.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.51,0:18:52.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.07,0:18:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么 你这小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.11,0:19:01.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是放羊的 应该知道我是怀着什么心情在找小七的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.43,0:19:04.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷走羊之后还想装不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.24,0:19:06.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么装不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:10.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是那样呢 不听辩解就说我们是小偷 太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.31,0:19:13.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么 小矮子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.52,0:19:15.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听彼得解释清楚就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.24,0:19:20.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你啊 住在阿鲁姆老头家里的那个女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.58,0:19:24.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪老头的孙女果然很倔强
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.81,0:19:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么怪老头
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.67,0:19:32.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这山谷附近可没有人不知道怪老头的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.64,0:19:35.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然说爷爷的坏话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:38.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 是又怎样 偷羊贼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:41.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住口 不要找借口了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.68,0:19:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.79,0:19:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来就是么 自己疏忽大意把羊弄丢了 都是你自己的错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.69,0:19:51.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那什么啊 还带个花环
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.83,0:19:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你带这东西 还和女孩子过家家 居然还能放羊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.59,0:20:00.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.03,0:20:03.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是 我也有帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.05,0:20:04.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.66,0:20:09.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我亲手给彼得做的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.36,0:20:12.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弄碎了又怎样 我打你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.26,0:20:13.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.63,0:20:17.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.24,0:20:21.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.32,0:20:19.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼 疼 好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.09,0:20:25.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你小子 太嚣张了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.58,0:20:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.86,0:20:42.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快 快松口 让你快松开啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.36,0:20:53.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要打了 不要打了 我们有约瑟夫 打架才不会输给你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.11,0:20:55.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约瑟夫 那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.10,0:21:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是狗啦 比你还要大一倍的狗 非常吓人的 就在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.00,0:21:09.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里呢 你说的狗在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.10,0:21:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不会上当呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.79,0:21:21.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约瑟夫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.39,0:21:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是约瑟夫来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:33.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救 救命啊 救命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.16,0:21:39.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约瑟夫 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.98,0:21:43.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小七 小七
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.47,0:21:47.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小七 快过来 小七
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.54,0:21:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小七
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.28,0:21:52.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧 快过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.74,0:21:56.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小七 快点 小七
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.97,0:22:27.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了 约瑟夫 看样子是下过雨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.50,0:22:31.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来 爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.72,0:22:36.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去村里了？\N恩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.64,0:22:39.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天多亏了约瑟夫才得救
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.71,0:22:42.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约瑟夫\N恩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.83,0:22:44.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.21,0:22:47.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也咬了他
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.18,0:22:51.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.23,0:22:56.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.20,0:22:59.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村里带的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.14,0:23:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.56,0:23:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.06,0:23:09.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山上到底发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.20,0:23:13.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 好看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.44,0:23:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好看 海蒂
